#### Setup

```{r}
rm(list = ls())
library(tidyverse)
library(here)

```

## Do your data viz worst

```{r}
# Read in data ----
space_launches <- read_csv(here("data", "space_launches.csv"))
```

```{r}
#| eval: false
# Check it out ----
skim(space_launches)
dim(space_launches)
summary(space_launches)
```

